<taxonomicNameLabel id="A2613B05FFEDFFB465DC6EB9FDBDBEFB" box="[451,527,1925,1946]" pageId="6" pageNumber="109" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
(10) Aedeagus in lateral view, scale bar = 0.1 mm. Figs 11-13. 
